  "category": "multi-hop",
  "question": "What is the homeworld of the Jedi Master who trained Ben Solo?",
  "answer": "Ben Solo (Kylo Ren) was trained by his uncle, Jedi Master **Luke Skywalker**. In canon, Luke's homeworld is **Tatooine**, where he was raised by Owen and Beru Lars after being separated from his twin sister Leia (who was raised on Alderaan).\n\nIn Legends continuity, Luke was likewise raised on Tatooine, though he was actually born on the asteroid colony of **Polis Massa** — Tatooine being the world he came to call home.",
